  "env_id": "wger_env@0.1",
  "description": "You are logged into wger fitness manager at http://localhost as the admin user (username: admin, password: adminadmin). In the 'University Athlete Menu' nutrition plan, create a new meal named 'Performance Bowl (25 Servings)' by scaling the four ingredients from the 'Performance Bowl (1 Serving)' meal by a factor of 25. Do not modify or delete the original meal.",
